WEBVTT

00:07:02.654 --> 00:07:05.258
And you don't see any security.

00:07:05.282 --> 00:07:08.701
And this was nine months
after terrible terrorist bombings

00:07:08.725 --> 00:07:10.672
that had ripped London apart.

00:07:10.696 --> 00:07:12.863
So I began to wonder
whether it was possible

00:07:12.887 --> 00:07:17.054
to do this kind of stuff
in even more complicated circumstances.

00:07:17.078 --> 00:07:19.804
We turned our attention
to Northern Ireland,

00:07:19.828 --> 00:07:22.420
the North of Ireland,
depending on your point of view.

00:07:22.444 --> 00:07:26.753
This is a map of England,
Scotland, Wales and Ireland,

00:07:26.777 --> 00:07:28.416
the island to the left.

00:07:28.829 --> 00:07:31.625
For generations,
it's been a place of conflict,